Class DatasetMetadataCollector

  • java.lang.Object
    • search.management.DatasetMetadataCollector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class DatasetMetadataCollector
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
    Dataset metadata collector. Collects all dataset metadata of a Dataset and therefore, their RecordReplica, DatasetFile. Also, implements Runnable to download in separated thread.
    Author:
    Karem Terry
